- A new shortcut to the Air Obelisk north of Edgeville.

- The Wilderness herb patch will never become diseased.

- +1% chance for double progress smithing bane, elder rune.

Unlimited teleports to Bork's lair.

- Receive 5% extra experience and renown in the Artisan's workshop.

Two feathers at once from the Phoenix.
Boosted stats on the ancient staff.
Granite buyer at the quarry and a new sandstone rock on the coast near Sophanem.

- 50% more Prayer XP from burning vyrewatch.
- 20% chance of creating a 4-dose prayer renewal potion when making it in Morytania.
- 10% additional Slayer XP for kills in the Slayer Tower when on a task.
- Double mushroom yield on the patch near Canifis.

name: Karamja Set Tasks - Elite
description: Given by any jungle forester north of Kharazi Jungle for completing all Elite Tasks in Karamja.
reward:

- 25% chance of receiving double tickets in Brimhaven Agility Arena.
- Once per day, if I am killed in the Fight Cave/Pit, I will be resurrected on the spot.
Double damage against wild dogs in Brimhaven Dungeon, and access to a shortcut to the red dragon area of the dungeon.
Lapalok will give me more Slayer points.
Once per day, the TzHaar banker will give me 8,000 Tok-Kul and Dell Monti will give me 40 apples.
I can now use the shortcut into Shilo village.

Increased chance of activating the special effect of an enchanted bolt.
Geoffrey in the flax field near Seers' Village will give you 200 flax per day.

- Unlimited teleports to the centre of Rellekka market.

- Unlimited teleports to the Farming patch north of Ardougne.
- Recharge 100% of your Summoning points once per day.
- The least valuable rewards from the Fishing Trawler will now be more valuable.
- 5% chance of smithing two rune crossbow limbs at once in Yanille.
- Guaranteed chance of two chompy birds appearing when chompy hunting.

name: Tirannwn Set Tasks - Elite
description: Given by Elen at the Max Guild for completing all Elite Tasks in Tirannwn.
reward:

- Daily logs from Coeden; a chance to not use charges on a most wanted card; 5% damage boost against dark beasts.
- 5% chance of not using a charge on your attuned crystal bow and wards.

- Ability to take a portrait at the photo booth with the head of one of the 8 elf lords.
- Double the blossoms harvested from the crystal acorn tree.

- Access to Daemonheim hard mode.

- Second gatestone and teleport spell.
